9 license under this subtitle, the [Governor’s] Office of Small, Minority, and Women Business
10 Affairs, in consultation with the Office of the Attorney General and the sports wagering
11 licensee, shall establish a clear plan for setting reasonable and appropriate minority
12 business enterprise participation goals and procedures for the procurement of goods and
13 services related to sports wagering, including procurement of construction, equipment, and
14 ongoing services.
15 (ii) To the extent practicable, the goals and procedures specified in
16 subparagraph (i) of this paragraph shall be based on the requirements of Title 14, Subtitle
17 3 of the State Finance and Procurement Article and the regulations implementing that
18 subtitle.
